profile:
At Gravity Electrical there is no job too big, too small or too complicated that we won’t complete. As an electrical company in Calgary, we provide our clients with quality work that is completed with the most advanced technology, and latest trends in the electrical field. By working with only the best technicians we know we can provide our customers with exceptional customer service and high-quality product from our first meeting to our final touch. We are not happy until you are! 

If you are looking for a residential electrician to help upgrade your electrical work, or maybe you need a security system installed, you can count on our expert team to show up on time and complete the job in the most effective manner without lowering our high-standard of product. Our well-trained technicians can handle new home wiring, alarm system installation, home cinema wiring and a long list of additional residential services. With years of experience and commitment to the local community, we have earned our status as the residential electrician Calgary calls first.

If it is a reliable commercial electrician you are looking for, you can count on us to bring our years of electrical expertise to each project. Our commercial electrician services can help you create an up-to-date electrical system for new construction projects, upgrade the wiring in an older building, or correct wiring mistakes in a property you’ve purchased. Our professionals have years of experience working with new constructions, as well as buildings of all sizes and designs. With our extensive knowledge, and years of experience, you should consider us your Calgary electrician for commercial needs. 

With our high quality work, customer service, and expert team of electricians, we have built a reputation as one of the most trustworthy electrical companies in Calgary. Whether your electrical needs are big or small, we are your solution!

profile:
Established in 2016, Halat Electric LTD. strives to provide exceptional services in Calgary and surrounding areas. We believe not only in providing top-quality services, but also in building strong relationships with our clients so that the words honest, reliable, and trustworthy come to mind when they think of us. 
To us, it's not just a 9-to-5 job; electrical is our passion. It's our passion to light up a room, it's our passion to see a client's face light up (no pun intended) when a job exceeds their imagination, and it's our passion to help make a house a home. 
We started Halat Electric LTD. because we were tired of hearing stories about clients being taken advantage of by contractors. High-quality electrical had to be made an affordable luxury to all. For this reason, we take pride in pricing all services with the client in mind. At Halat Electric LTD. we're proud to be the contractor that clients can trust and rely on to deliver quality work.
services:
At Halat Electric LTD., we offer all types of electrical services; from residential to commercial renovations and developments. We also specialize in Smart Home systems. Our residential services include, but are not limited to, home developments, such as new home or basement developments, pot light installation, service panel upgrades, garage development, and servicing faulty electrical systems and equipment. 

Our commercial services include, but are also not limited to; new commercial developments and renovations, and servicing faulty systems and equipment.
